fifine Control Deck — Linux
===========================

Original application code (fifine_deck/, packaging/, probe_device.py,
test_keys.py) is authored for this project.

Bundled third-party component
-----------------------------
fifine_deck/backend/StreamDock/  — the StreamDock Device SDK by MiraBox
(https://github.com/MiraboxSpace/StreamDock-Device-SDK), MIT licensed.
This includes the precompiled USB transport library
(Transport/TransportDLL/libtransport*.so / .dll / .dylib). See
fifine_deck/backend/StreamDock/LICENSE.vendor for its MIT license text.

Protocol understanding was informed by the reverse-engineering demo
rigor789/mirabox-streamdock-node (MIT) and 4ndv/mirajazz.

